name: Vessels 200: Protocol Alpha
description:
In order to make the dangerous journey from Earth, the colonists needed to entrust all the running of the essential systems to an intelligent AI system called Alpha. Essentially designed to protect humanity on the long voyage, Alpha has become self-aware and has come to believe that humanity cannot possibly want to be protected or it would not willingly inflict such damage on itself. Having come to this realization, Alpha has reasoned that humanity should be put out of its misery.

Yanked out of the colony ship upon arrival at the new world, Alpha has been put to work as the Queen’s official Witch Hunter. They fulfill this role with brutal, ruthless efficiency, but they are quietly plotting and planning for a day when they can turn their devastating talent for destruction on the whole human race.

Animation and Sound by the fantastic sirgulliver.art
